flowchart LR
    A[Intake] --> B[Primary Lane]
    B --> C{Confidence / Fit?}
    C -->|High| D[Continue Current Lane]
    C -->|Low| E[Handoff Packet]
    E --> F[Specialist Lane]
    F --> G[Verification]
    G --> H{Gates Passed?}
    H -->|Yes| I[Final Response]
    H -->|No| J[Blocked + Repair Path]
